			<abstract>
				<title>Abstract</title>
				<p>In this paper we present a survey of numericalmethods for optimal control problems governed by convection-diffusion equations. For ease of exposition we focus on stationary convection-diffusion optimal control problems with distributed control. Several effective numericalmethods including stabilizedmethods and discontinuous Galerkinmethods are reviewed. Furthermore, we also make some investigations about convection-diffusion optimal control problems with state constraints and pointwisely imposed control.</p>
